<h3>ISSUE: Sync Systems only for Expanded Case Type</h3>
<p>When Sync Systems is checked, a user cannot sync another Case Type without first unchecking and checking the Sync check box.</p>
<h4>SOLUTION: Expand Sync display to all Case Types</h4>
<p>As long as the Sync Systems check box is checked, all Smartflows will display the Sync options regardless of the Case Type selected.</p>
